@startuml
title Figure 7. DocuTracker Administrator Sequence

actor Administrator as Admin
participant "DocuTracker App" as App
participant "Server" as Server
database Database

Admin -> App : **1.** Open Admin settings
App -> Server : **2.** Load current config
Server -> Database : **3.** Read workflows\nand permissions
Database --> App : **4.** Show settings

Admin -> App : **5.** Save workflow steps
App -> Server : **6.** Save new workflow version
Server -> Database : **7.** Store steps\nand assignees
Database --> App : **8.** Saved

Admin -> App : **9.** Set user permissions
App -> Server : **10.** Save permission rules
Server -> Database : **11.** Store permissions
Database --> App : **12.** Saved

Admin -> App : **13.** View overdue documents
App -> Server : **14.** Request overdue list
Server -> Database : **15.** Query overdue records
Database --> App : **16.** Display list

@enduml
